The increased transmissibility of these VOCs has been documented, but knowledge about their virulence is limited. Methods: We created a retrospective cohort of people in Ontario who tested positive for SARS-CoV-2 and were screened for VOCs, with dates of test report between Feb. 7 and June 27, 2021.
